             was indicted for <rs id="t18290219-67-off363" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18290219-67-off363" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290219-67-off363" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18290219-67-cd364" type="crimeDate">16th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290219-67-off363 t18290219-67-cd364"></join>, 1 watch, value 20s.; 1 pair of trousers, value 3s.; 1 purse, value 1d.; 12 shillings, and 16 sixpences
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18290219-67-victim669" type="victimName">
                     Benjamin Christopher 
                     Wenlock
                  <interp inst="t18290219-67-victim669" type="surname" value="Wenlock"></interp>
